{"type":"message","id":"e82fc748","parentId":"f61c6c5d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T09:15:41.460Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The context monitor detected that context usage is at 62%, exceeding the 60% threshold. According to the context manager skill, when the threshold is reached, it should automatically create a new session with loaded memory. Let me check the skill to see what the proper action is.","thinkingSignature":"147bbd2cc007bd380e2ff4e473463c95d42dd605b4d6261ea0cab05d128372fb"},{"type":"text","text":"Context usage is at **62%** (123,375/200,000 tokens), exceeding the 60% threshold.\n\nAccording to the context manager skill, when threshold is reached, it should automatically create a new session with loaded memory. However, this is a cron-triggered script that only logs the alert.\n\nFor now, the alert has been logged. If you'd like me to:\n1. **Start a new session** to reset context (with memory loaded)\n2. **Increase the threshold** (current: 60%)\n3. **Do nothing** and continue in current session\n\nWhat would you prefer?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1277,"output":184,"cacheRead":37011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38472,"cost":{"input":0.0003831,"output":0.0002208,"cacheRead":0.0011103299999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017142299999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773911721186}}
